{"tid":1947848,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 禁止群體聚集規例全文","createTime":"2020-03-28T14:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T14:24:23.000Z","uid":99828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"481760a0ee8e3b03a4a3c90874549a6431d47173","tid":1947848,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"政府憲報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202417e/cs22020241732.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202417e%2Fcs22020241732.pdf&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq7CEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=c64a8794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202417e/cs22020241732.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"7c26030c6166856e5dea3057111bc27021c4135a","tid":1947848,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnuVUav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnuVUav.jpg&h=d45808d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e298777b2d941380e7c3a683f4646c043ed32f0e","tid":1947848,"uid":99828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"重點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 四人以上，喺公眾地方聚集就係犯法，除非係十二項豁免之內<br />\n2.  參與聚集, 組織聚集同擁有、控制或營運進行該聚集的地方及明知而容許該聚集進行嘅人都犯法<br />\n3. 如果執法人員有合理理由相信有人犯咗呢條法，可以要求你提供其姓名、出生日期、地址及聯絡電話號碼，同埋進入和巡查公眾地方<br />\n4. 規例在 2020 年 6 月 28 日午夜失效"}]}